text: Coeloprocta humeralis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1940. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Coeloprocta humeralis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1940
